{"tid":1978803,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國國務卿批評香港民主派人士被捕事件，憂慮屬政治化執法","createTime":"2020-04-19T03:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T05:25:19.000Z","uid":134071,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b9241d7d70a621bfade409c7522a00a42d18110b","tid":1978803,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T03:49:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521436-20200419.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521436-20200419.htm&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDnfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=791ca6e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521436-20200419.htm&h=386b5410\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521436-20200419.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧批評本港多名民主派人士被拘捕事件，說對他們表示深切關注。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧在社交網站表示，香港民主派人士被捕，令人深感憂慮，認為是政治化的執法行動，與言論及和平集會自由的普遍價值觀相矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n眾議院議長波洛西也表示，即使全球正面臨新型冠狀病毒危機，香港民主與人權仍繼續遭到攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n美國國會及行政部門中國問題委員會主席麥高文呼籲總統特朗普，儘快開始執行《香港人權與民主法案》。<br />\n<br />\n麥高文說，在全球疫情大流行之際，對香港民主派人士的拘捕行動十分不合理。香港人權與民主被侵犯的情況日益惡化，特朗普政府應強力執行《香港人權與民主法案》。<br />\n<br />\n共和黨籍的參議院多數黨領袖麥康奈爾也說，不容許中共利用疫情大流行掩飾拘捕和平民主領袖，說「我們與香港站在一起」。"},{"pid":"09f8857aef3674b523e6b1881ef7d6d16a434ea5","tid":1978803,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T03:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />tweeted"},{"pid":"d42ca47a9f3eae3199cb2cf93684301791416a93","tid":1978803,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09f8857aef3674b523e6b1881ef7d6d16a434ea5","tid":1978803,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T03:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />tweeted"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T03:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/SecPompeo/status/1251622578478886912\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FSecPompeo%2Fstatus%2F1251622578478886912&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDnfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=c1e7643e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/SecPompeo/status/1251622578478886912</a>"},{"pid":"af5738f186a56996e5b59992af7c1041b46ccf17","tid":1978803,"uid":228868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acaf16ae4a3f53216c0a67749941cb8c2c4957fe","tid":1978803,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7d2ddd110cba73bd005a1cb7df56792d51fdf7","tid":1978803,"uid":235501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:07:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"051e157ed5dbd85a078b4982a5c1eec2f929bb57","tid":1978803,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac388c6069a3c6036e6d99c2ee5f6394b95febb0","tid":1978803,"uid":269372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:10:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ki